{"tid":1713034,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"求下你地黎明行動唔好搞馬路d坑渠蓋","createTime":"2019-11-12T16:06:28.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-12T16:11:40.000Z","uid":150625,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"a77ad18da09f72748d60f6a403766f11726e4b7c","tid":1713034,"uid":150625,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T16:06:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-dQOTJMs4H7E/U4FSJXS5wHI/AAAAAAABE3g/5qwKfWcP7So/s1600/Inspection+Cover_PCCW.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2F3.bp.blogspot.com%2F-dQOTJMs4H7E%2FU4FSJXS5wHI%2FAAAAAAABE3g%2F5qwKfWcP7So%2Fs1600%2FInspection%2BCover_PCCW.JPG&h=ba9b6a76&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 作為一隻港豬我好鐘意返工架<br />\n但如果大家邊日一朝早搵大型十字鐵筆抽起左重要大馬路既坑渠蓋<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.orangenews.hk/pic/0/10/18/52/10185238_986957.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.orangenews.hk%2Fpic%2F0%2F10%2F18%2F52%2F10185238_986957.jpg&h=0395090f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n仲要將個蓋唔知收左去邊冇得好快蓋返<br />\n條路好危險完全唔可以行車架<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">真係起左蓋一定要set危險警告牌</span></span><br />\n<br />\n渠蓋失蹤現大窿公路索命 積架中招 全車報銷 渠署靠害<br />\n<a href=\"https://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/news/20180220/00174_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Forientaldaily.on.cc%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180220%2F00174_001.html&d=QaIhKqS2ROfvs0VeIWBCOm5ZeM81ILqxQ%2BPX7M1Kayg%3D&h=f820bf8e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/news/20180220/00174_001.html</a><br />\n<br />\n爛渠蓋劏爆胎六車輪陷<br />\n<a href=\"http://the-sun.on.cc/cnt/news/20140425/00407_047.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fthe-sun.on.cc%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20140425%2F00407_047.html&d=QaIhKqS2ROfvs0VeIWBCOm5ZeM81ILqxQ%2BPX7M1Kayg%3D&h=e5e43511\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://the-sun.on.cc/cnt/news/20140425/00407_047.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n個蓋唔見既話仲要唔知幾多日先搞掂<br />\nd路因為安全問題封晒我點返工呀 尤其地鐵又同時比你地塞住既話<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/22.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />求下你地唔好呀"},{"pid":"1b4e9f887acedd5315112aef248b3705ce220062","tid":1713034,"uid":337761,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T16:06:42.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: orange;\">入去retweet like reply</span><br />\n最新：Hawley 出第二條關於中大的tweet!<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/HawleyMO/status/1194269562608463879?s=20\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FHawleyMO%2Fstatus%2F1194269562608463879%3Fs%3D20&d=QaIhKqS2ROfvs0VeIWBCOm5ZeM81ILqxQ%2BPX7M1Kayg%3D&h=525c2fbe\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FHawleyMO%2Fstatus%2F1194269562608463879%3Fs%3D20&h=dd03ffb2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/HawleyMO/status/1194269562608463879?s=20</a><br />\n<br />\n第一條<br />\n（twitter 突發）美國參議員Hawley 為警察攻入中大校園出聲啦！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1712330\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1712330</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n第二條<br />\nLuke de Pulford鬧爆警察射頭<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/lukedepulford/status/1194146831086829569?s=19\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Flukedepulford%2Fstatus%2F1194146831086829569%3Fs%3D19&d=QaIhKqS2ROfvs0VeIWBCOm5ZeM81ILqxQ%2BPX7M1Kayg%3D&h=7e6ce461\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Flukedepulford%2Fstatus%2F1194146831086829569%3Fs%3D19&h=4c21951e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/lukedepulford/status/1194146831086829569?s=19</a><br />\n<br />\n更加多嘅任務同link去 @TwitterHelpBot，admin團隊會繼續更新。"},{"pid":"920176c199e0a2d6321634b81f30308ee5be9f3c","tid":1713034,"uid":150625,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T16:07:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8bbcb7d6d9bd67a42f60e896d243c37401ebb778","tid":1713034,